CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 2, 1958, pg. A12, reads: "The FROGS Have Fun - Frog Week opened last Sunday with a gay party for members, their wives and out-of-town guests at the Terrain Room of Terrace Hall.  The above pictures tell the story of how the Frogs and their guests had fun... - All Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Men, including Morris Fountain, Sr. on right, singing around microphone, at FROGS week party in Terrain Room of Terrace Hall
